   IMPLEMENTING OF WORD GUESSING GAME
The steps to run the application seem to be as follows:
1.	Navigate to the directory containing the Python file word_guessing_app.py using the command prompt.
2.	Run the command streamlit run word_guessing_app.py to start the Streamlit application.
3.	The command prompt will display the local and network URLs where the application can be accessed.
4.	Open the provided local URL (e.g., http://localhost:8501) in a web browser to access the word guessing game interface.
Commond to run:
cd "C:\Users\hemav\OneDrive\Documents\Guessing_the_word"
streamlit run word_guessing_app.py
You can now view your Streamlit app in your browser.

  Local URL: http://localhost:8501
  Network URL: http://192.168.92.77:8501
